  "subject": "[SDNC] Fixes to aaiclient.properties",
  "commit_message": "[SDNC] Fixes to aaiclient.properties\n\nThis change fixes the issue seen where SDNC is trying to reach\nAAI via aai.api.simpledemo.onap.org endpoint.  The root cause was\nthat the mount for the aaiclient.properties file was incorrect\n(ccsdkConfigDir instead of configDir), causing that version to\nbe ignored in favor of the version bundled into the docker image.\n\nIssue-ID: SDNC-1354\nSigned-off-by: Dan Timoney <dtimoney@att.com>\nChange-Id: Ib9f9f51fd36150f2fe82323a767b28703a1a9390\n",
